value.name: Post Traumatic Quest: My Quest to Transcend Trauma, Turn My Pain into Purpose, and Find Peace
value.description: Check out this great listen on Audible.com. From pain to purpose, purpose to peace. In 1999, Danny Sanchez was an inmate in San Quentin Prison. In 2012, he was commended for his work in youth violence prevention and named a Champion of Change by President Barak Obama.
